text: Erkki Rajala (12 March 1923 - 5 December 1977) was a Finnish ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1948 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1923 births Category:1977 deaths Category:Finnish male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Finland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1948 Winter Olympics Category:People from Orimattila
